{"tid":1590100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼佬警司英文都唔識 學人用英文","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T03:14:39.000Z","uid":74303,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4be0d5ddf417d03aa5c4996b2df9375d40ba5f","tid":1590100,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4dwHFs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4dwHFs.png&h=05c65579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係可悲，我當去母語唔係英文，但係嚟香港做嘢咁高級，written英文都用到一舊舊<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;These zombies would believe anything these Pan<br />\nDems tell them no matter how ridiculous and contrary to the truth&rdquo; 根本grammar錯曬<br />\n<br />\n1. &ldquo;Anything&rdquo; 帶<span style=\"color: red;\">negative</span>意思，需要用係negative sentence：<br />\nI do <span style=\"color: red;\">not</span> believe anything you&rsquo;ve said. 就啱因為句子裡面有 not<br />\n<br />\n正確應該係 &ldquo;these zombies would believe <span style=\"color: gold;\">everything</span> these Pan Dems tell them&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. No matter 句式錯誤<br />\ne.g. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Stay positive no matter how tired </span><span style=\"color: red;\">you are</span>.<br />\n因為no matter 之後已經係第二個clause，可以當另外一句咁睇，所以no matter需要有齊英文短句裡面所需要有嘅subject verb object<br />\n<br />\n正確寫法：<br />\nThese zombies would believe everything these Pan Dems tell them no matter how ridiculous and contradictory it is to the truth<br />\n<br />\n呢啲英文係三年級都識嘅簡單英文，啲黑警扮人講英文以為自己好勁"},{"pid":"fa0d4a334251c6ec04b28f8259bb0ace54a9bb7c","tid":1590100,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"d34c0c11b92d006f3d727bbe3462e5323f50ea76","tid":1590100,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士及死難者<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係中共嘅紀念日落鳩佢面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse